Description: ==========
        Torsession
        ==========
        
        :Info: Torsession is an asynchronous session backend with Mongodb for Tornado
        :Author: Lime YH.Shi
        
        .. image:: https://pypip.in/v/torsession/badge.png
                :target: https://crate.io/packages/torsession
        
        .. image:: https://pypip.in/d/torsession/badge.png
                :target: https://crate.io/packages/torsession
        
        
        Installation
        ============
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ pip install torsession
        
        Example
        =======
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            # Initialize SessionManager
            sm = SessionManager(motor.MotorClient())
        
            # create a new session or load a session
            session = yield sm.new_session()
            session = yield sm.load_session("session id")
        
            # set a key-value pair
            yield session.set(key, value)
        
            # get key
            yield session.get(key)
        
            # delete a key
            yield session.delete(key)
        
            # refresh session id
            yield session.refresh_id()
        
            # clear a session
            yield session.clear()
        
        
